  m_Name: D2FR Dialogue
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: 
  dialogueHidesSubmit: 1
  lines:
  - You Aleks?
  - 'You: Huh? Uh, yeah, why?'
  - "Perfect. I\u2019m a member of a faction of guys that don\u2019t buy into the
    lies of this here government, believe you met our top guy yesterday."
  - "We\u2019re all the same age, old enough to remember our life before that day
    we were \u201Csaved\u201D."
  - "Doesn\u2019t quite feel like we were \u201Csaved\u201D though, does it? You\u2019re
    our age too, so you should remember enough to think there was more to that day,
    right?"
  - "You: I\u2026.. I believe I do. But they\u2019ve never done us any wrong, so
    why conspire?"
  - "In that case, shouldn\u2019t be surprising that we\u2019re thinking they have
    a bigger plan to this whole evacuation thing."
  - 'Give this a look. '
  - "\u201CWe built it to protect you all from outsiders\u201D, nothing about that
    on it is there? They\u2019ve clearly been hiding info from us, and who knows
    what else."
  - "This plan of theres, it\u2019s certain to effect not just you, but your family
    too."
  - "We need your help, our internet access we need for investigating is gone, only
    you border control lot still have it up, and you\u2019re our only suitable candidate
    to help us."
  - Will you?
  - "You: \u2026. If it puts my daughter in no danger, I\u2019ll do it"
  - "I\u2019ll make sure of it. We\u2019ll be in touch later, keep an eye out."
  bridgeAfterDialogue: 0
